{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_04_03",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 3話 あ～んして下さい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏フェス当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of Summer Festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日のライブで、いよいよ新曲初披露だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's live performance will finally debut the new song‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "曲作りに苦労した分、いい曲が出来ましたから\nファンの反応が楽しみです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We put a lot of effort into composing‚ so we came up with a great song.\nI'm looking forward to the fans' reactions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 12.3778001945
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "何しろ今度の新曲は、四人で夏を楽しんだ経験が\n元になって出来たんですからね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ this new song was inspired by the experiences of\nthe four of us enjoying the summer together~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 19.1847618898
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "新曲が夏で浮かれてはしゃぐ人達にもの申す\nって感じなのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It gives off a vibe of telling off those who frolic around\nin summer with the new song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.033538241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "きっと莉央さんは合宿中に相当腹の立つことが\nあったんだろうな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure Rio-san had quite a few things\nto be angry about during the training camp…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 29.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "それはまぁ、いろいろと……\nでもかっこいい曲になったと思いませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's… in various ways…\nBut don't you think it became a cool song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 36.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "確かにリズノワらしい刺激的でかっこいい曲だ\nこころも頑張った甲斐があったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ it's an exciting and cool song befitting of LizNoir.\nYour efforts paid off‚ Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "合宿中、こころがみんなの役に立とうとしていた姿を\n俺はちゃんと見ていたぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During the training camp‚\nI saw you trying to be helpful to everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 48.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "うふふ～、もっと褒めていいんですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe~ You can praise me more‚ you know~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 52.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "夏合宿のおかげで素晴らしい曲が出来たので、実質\nこころが新曲を作ったと言っても過言じゃありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to the summer training camp‚ we were able to create an amazing song‚\nso it's not an exaggeration to say that Kokoro practically composed the new song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それは過言だろ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's an exaggeration…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 62.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄では楽しくて刺激的で\n忘れられない思い出が沢山出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In Okinawa‚ we had a lot of fun and exciting moments‚\nand I made unforgettable memories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんには感謝してるんです\n忙しいのに合宿について来てくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm grateful to you‚ {user}-san‚\nfor coming along on the training camp despite being busy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 75.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと見守っててくれたから\nこころは安心してやりたいことが出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been watching over me the whole time‚\nand that gave Kokoro the peace of mind to do what I wanted to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "いざとなったら全部{user}さんの\nせいにすればいいんだって思ったら心強かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When things got tough‚\nI felt relieved thinking that I could just put the blame on {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 87.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "問題が起こらなくて本当に良かったよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad nothing troublesome happened…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 90.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんも先輩方と沢山遊んで楽しそうでした\n合宿大成功です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai-chan seemed to have a lot of fun playing with the senpais too.\nThe camp was a great success!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、リズノワの結束も\n一層深まったんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ LizNoir's bond\nprobably grew even stronger‚ didn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 101.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　それで、お礼をしたいんですけど\nちょっと付き合ってもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! So‚ I want to thank you properly.\nCan you spare some time for that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 107.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "お礼なんて気にしなくていいから……って\n今から出かける気か？　もうすぐリハーサルだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to worry about thanking me…\nAre you planning to go out now? Rehearsals will start soon‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワの出番まで時間があるから大丈夫ですよ～\nさあさあ、行きますよ、ついて来て下さ～い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We still have some time until LizNoir's turn‚ so it's okay~.\nCome on‚ come on‚ let's go~! Follow me~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5933.333333299998,
          "startTime": 120.8333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8766.66666669999,
          "startTime": 123.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 123.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 123.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "衣装のまま出歩くのはまずいだろ\nこころだとバレたら大騒ぎになるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not good to walk around in your outfit like this.\nIf they recognize you as Kokoro‚ it'll cause a big commotion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "この後ステージで歌うアイドルが\n屋台で買い食いしてるなんて誰も思いませんよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No one would think that an idol who\nwill sing on stage later is eating at food stalls~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 136.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "こういうのは堂々としてる方が\nかえってバレないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's actually less likely\nto get noticed if you act openly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
