      "text": "それにしたって堂々とし過ぎだ。もしかして\n今までも本番前に買い食いしたことがあるんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ you're being too open about it. Have you ever done\nsomething like eating at food stalls before a performance…?",
